# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ Forgetting to update the loop variable.

```java
int i = 1;

while(i <= 5){
    System.out.println(i);
}
```

Infinite loop.

---

❌ Incorrect condition.

```java
int i = 10;

while(i <= 1){
    System.out.println(i);
}
```

Loop never executes.

