# Revision Box

✅ while → Repeats while the condition is true.

✅ Best when iterations are unknown.

✅ Update the loop variable.

✅ while(true) → Infinite loop.

✅ Sentinel value → Special value that terminates the loop.

✅ O(n) → Depends on input size.

✅ O(1) → Fixed number of iterations.

